<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī jayābhyudaya śālivā 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>hana śakha varṣaṁbbulu 1591 A 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>gunēṭi prabhava saṁvvatsara śrāvaṇa 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ba ḷa 10 lu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīmatu poṁnamareḍi caṁ 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>nnāreḍi Āpoṭipāpireḍigāru vēyiṁccina 
<lb n="6"/>vana dharmaśāsanaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> boḍitippanapalleku dakṣa 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṇa bhagamuna meḍidiṁnna trōvanu 
<lb n="8"/>vuṁnnavanaṁ krayānaku tīsuka sū 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ryanārāyaṇārpaṇaṁgānu 
<lb n="10"/>vēIṁccina vana śāsanamu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> 
<lb n="11"/>vaṭipali cēnu bhaṭagāriki sū 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ryanārāyaṇārpitaṁgānu 
<lb n="13"/>reṁḍu ciṁttaceṭlu yiccināramu śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> 
</p>

